{"tid":991700,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人因為驚分手所以唔同嗰個人開始?","createTime":"2019-01-22T14:38:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T17:51:13.000Z","uid":64838,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e3ba9b515a8bc72f80320b143dc068e30c846185","tid":991700,"uid":64838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:38:04.000Z","msg":"最近同個識左好耐嘅朋友開始有啲曖昧<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地性格興趣個啲都好夾<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日ff同佢一齊嘅畫面<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢啲朋友都暗示我去馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢就有一樣性格我唔係咁鍾意,覺得一齊嘅話會長久唔到,<br />\n會寧願一世做好好嘅朋友都唔想分手之後大家毫無關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人明我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44aa7ab26ec6eba89624eff4425bfcc0badfe2e6","tid":991700,"uid":106848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:39:23.000Z","msg":"我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14be2e51714f6a2648ca436f02662c7997dfb1ff","tid":991700,"uid":31522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:41:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bef0bceed0de4b8c0ece3787fa78e1f487ade75b","tid":991700,"uid":64838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14be2e51714f6a2648ca436f02662c7997dfb1ff","tid":991700,"uid":31522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:41:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce6cef3906477a8f87aa39642c3e2e931adcf36","tid":991700,"uid":210161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T14:48:06.000Z","msg":"明<br />\n你搞曖味 搞到咁上下就唔想有下一步<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br /